<dd>Hypocrisy much?<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Batvette" title="User:Batvette">Batvette</a> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Batvette" title="User talk:Batvette">talk</a>) 07:42, 29 October 2012 (UTC)</dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
