<p>"Apart from a single mention of stalking early on, the article is about paranoid delusions of mind control, not about stalking."  Now that I am suggesting stalking victims are not delusional you are changing your opinion?  I disagree, the article is inappropriate for a Stalking page.  And again, if the material referring to mind control delusions stays, it's inappropriate not to provide the contrary opinion which is clearly expressed throughout the article. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/65.7.161.239" title="Special:Contributions/65.7.161.239">65.7.161.239</a> (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:65.7.161.239" title="User talk:65.7.161.239">talk</a>) 04:17, 28 April 2013 (UTC) 
